snippet.title: Super Pocket Capcom & TAITO Edition!
snippet.description:
Two new retro gaming handhelds that give you world-renowned ARCADE GAMES IN YOUR POCKET!
 
ONLY £49/$59/€59 EACH!
 
Super Pocket Capcom Edition and Super Pocket TAITO Edition feature the games that you know and love, like Street Fighter II’: Hyper Fighting, Space Invaders, Final Fight, Bubble Bobble, Ghouls ‘N Ghosts, Rastan, and more in your hands!
 
PRE-ORDER FROM FRIDAY, JULY 14TH

AVAILABLE OCTOBER 2023

Sign up for our email newsletter here: https://www.hypermegatech.com
